{"tid":732084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國在南太平洋勢力增 紐西蘭：威脅國安","createTime":"2018-07-06T17:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T00:41:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89b6be70f902e556a1ebdd5a94211d9dda80468f","tid":732084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"中國在南太平洋勢力增 紐西蘭：威脅國安<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/416274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F416274&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4823b6df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/416274</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，紐西蘭政府今天(6日)公布一份國防報告，當中警告中國在南太平洋影響力增加，可能會破壞區域的穩定。此說可能引發中紐雙邊關係緊張。<br />\n<br />\n傳統上，紐西蘭與澳洲是南太平洋的兩大要角。但紐國這份國防報告卻指出，紐西蘭目前正在區域小島國之間失去影響力，輸給中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出：「紐西蘭國家安全仍與太平洋地區的穩定直接相關。隨著太平洋島國發展&hellip;諸如紐西蘭與澳洲等(小島國的)傳統夥伴，將在維持影響力上遭受挑戰。」「中國對人權與資訊自由的觀點，與紐西蘭盛行的觀點相違背。」<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭先前已宣布，將把對外援助增加近三分之一，部分原因便是要遏制中國在南太平洋日增的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭國防部長馬克(Ron Mark)也在威靈頓(Wellington)告訴記者：「我們生存在混沌的年代，世界正在改變，強權競爭已再度浮現。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對太平洋地區而言，澳洲是最大的援助提供者，今年就撥出1億6,640萬澳元(1億2,900萬美元)的資金。不過分析家指出，隨著澳洲出現龐大預算赤字，未來經濟援助預算將降到紀錄新低，為中國開放門戶。<br />\n</span><br />\n根據澳洲智庫羅伊研究院(The Lowy Institute)，中國對南太平洋的經濟援助正顯著增長，2016年的前十年，估計共投入17.8億美元。中方則否認使用援助計畫，來增強在南太平洋的影響力。"},{"pid":"87d76192d07b5ffb57bfea01842fd0af24bd85fd","tid":732084,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e46bd46ee6615e6b6675784b46581db692c8eb7","tid":732084,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"加入圍堵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70cf12fdd0ccd98063f757dab3f083cc72a6fa5","tid":732084,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"就快比人踢出five eyes <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688f8c7b3bb67bf7f5ea994abec9d873a8382b25","tid":732084,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e46bd46ee6615e6b6675784b46581db692c8eb7","tid":732084,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"加入圍堵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"聯軍又多一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dded4bfc3b9c9523abb4600a447f9c49840b2c1e","tid":732084,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"外交部未講都已經估到：這是維護中國領土主權，雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人幾時向北發展侵佔俄佬領土，光復大元國土。近代德國同法國都未攻入俄佬首都，幾時嚟番個創舉，以示中華國威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dd22e29eb116f4326259d60d0d7befbc61b366","tid":732084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0b230fae6a8b0511ed63638336ef2e78717d4e","tid":732084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cde2d3da93c1327f082fac8ea937916d09392f","tid":732084,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"又係贏國"},{"pid":"9c9ca78a2373c9109c1a88b23b19cae5a57d0f9f","tid":732084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T00:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}